'''Denis Sassou Nguesso''' (23 Ugushyingo 1943) ni Perezida wa [[Repubulika ya Kongo]]. 

Mu Kwakira 2021, Denis Sassou N'Guesso yavuzwe mu kibazo cy’urukozasoni rwa "Pandora Paper". Nk’uko ihuriro mpuzamahanga ry’abanyamakuru ribitangaza, mu 1998, nyuma gato yo gusubira ku butegetsi bwa Denis Sassou N'Guesso Ishoramari rya Inter African ryanditswe mu birwa bya Virginie y’Ubwongereza, ahantu h’imisoro ya Karayibe. Denis Sassou N'Guesso arahakana en bloc ni inyandiko.
